      { question: "Can I customize waivers for my studio?", answer: "Yes. InkFlow lets you build your own waiver template with your studio logo, custom fields (allergies, medical history, consent for photography, release for minors), conditional logic, and state-specific clauses. You can maintain multiple templates for different services (tattoo, piercing, PMU)." },
