      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-500">By <a href="/about" class="text-accent-400 hover:underline">{EEAT_AUTHOR.name}</a>, {EEAT_AUTHOR.title} · Reviewed by {EEAT_REVIEWER.name}, {EEAT_REVIEWER.title} · Updated {UPDATED}</p>
