        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="mx-auto flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-accent-600 text-xl font-bold text-white">1</div>
          <h3 class="mt-4 text-lg font-semibold text-white">Create Your Waiver Template</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-400">Use our visual editor or AI composer to build a tattoo-specific consent form. Add fields for medical history, design approval, photo consent, and minors. Support multiple templates for tattoo vs piercing vs PMU.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="mx-auto flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-accent-600 text-xl font-bold text-white">2</div>
          <h3 class="mt-4 text-lg font-semibold text-white">Share via QR Code or Link</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-400">Print a QR poster for the front desk, embed it on your website, or send a link via SMS/email before appointments. Clients open it in their browser — <strong class="text-white">no app download needed</strong>.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="mx-auto flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-accent-600 text-xl font-bold text-white">3</div>
          <h3 class="mt-4 text-lg font-semibold text-white">Client Signs, You Get a Court-Admissible PDF</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-400">Client signs in under 60 seconds. The signed PDF — with full audit trail (IP, timestamp, device fingerprint, SHA-256 hash) — lands in your dashboard and is sent to the client. ESIGN + UETA compliant.</p>
        </div>
