          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-400"><strong class="text-accent-400">Exclusive</strong>: After the waiver is signed, automatically send aftercare instructions via email/SMS. Turn a compliance requirement into a retention tool. <a href="/features/tattoo-aftercare-software-automation" class="text-accent-400 hover:underline">Learn more →</a></p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 bg-ink-900/50 p-5">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">Multi-Template Support</h3>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-400">Separate templates for tattoo, piercing, PMU, and minor waivers. Each with custom fields, state-specific clauses, and conditional logic.</p>
