        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-ink-800 bg-ink-900/50 p-5">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">✅ Data Privacy &amp; HIPAA Readiness</h3>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-400">Your clients' medical history and personal data are encrypted at rest and in transit. While tattoo studios are not typically HIPAA-covered entities, InkFlow follows HIPAA-level best practices for medical information handling. SOC 2 compliant infrastructure.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

