      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">What Studio Owners Say</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Real quotes from real tattoo studios. [Add your customer stories here — full name, studio name, Instagram handle].</p>
      <div class="mt-8 rounded-xl border border-ink-800 bg-ink-900/50 p-8">
        <blockquote class="text-lg italic text-gray-300">
          "[Replace with real customer quote — e.g.: We went from paper chaos to fully digital in one weekend. Our check-in time dropped from 5 minutes to 30 seconds, and our clients love that they can sign from their phone before they even walk in.]"
        </blockquote>
