        <div class="rounded-lg border border-ink-800 bg-ink-900/50 p-5">
          <h3 class="font-medium text-white">Can I customize waivers for my studio's specific needs?</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-400">Yes. InkFlow lets you build custom waiver templates with your studio logo, custom fields (allergies, medical history, design approval, photo consent), conditional logic (show different clauses for tattoo vs piercing), and state-specific compliance clauses. You can maintain multiple templates for different services.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-ink-800 bg-ink-900/50 p-5">
          <h3 class="font-medium text-white">What happens to signed waivers? Can I export them?</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-400">Every signed waiver is stored in your secure cloud dashboard with search by client name, date, or service type. You can export individual PDFs or batch export for annual audits or health department inspections. Clients also receive a copy via email. Waivers are retained per your state's statute of limitations, with automatic archival.</p>
